The paper deals with deep neural network training, specifically the hyper-parameter of learning rate. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of mutual information for layer-wise setting of learning rate, which could potentially relate to computer vision (cs.CV) or control systems (cs.SY).
